It felt like too much overhead. CommonRuntimeTest does not just recursively clean this directory, it also checks against its notion of dalvik cache and so on. So it would have been a non-trivial rewrite to make this non-static code static and accessible, whereas here we know there should be nothing in the tmp directory anymore.

