it feels a bit weird that we call "set environment variables" which implicitly creates a directory and then we remove the directory in a sub-class. Perhaps QuickTestSetup for SetEnvironmentVariables and QuickTestSetup for the teardown. I wonder we could see the unbalanced problem again without something more intention revealing.

